'm not sure what you value the most. Do you have a preference for any of the items?<|eot_id|><|start_header_id|>assistant<|end_header_id|>\n\nI'm actually more interested in the non-ring items. I think the dice and the pan could be quite valuable, but I'm not sure how you feel about them. Do you have a strong preference for either the dice or the pan?<|eot_id|><|start_header_id|>user<|end_header_id|>\n\nI'm not particularly interested in the pan, but I do think the dice could be useful. I'd be willing to let you have the pan if we can come to an agreement on the other items. What do you think about the rings? Would you be interested in taking one, or do you think I should take all of them?<|eot_id|><|start_header_id|>assistant<|end_header_id|>\n\nThat's a generous offer on the pan. As for the rings, I'm not particularly interested in them, so I think it would be fair if you took all three. In return, I'd like to propose that I take the pan and the dice. Would that be acceptable to you, or would you like to negotiate further?<|eot_id|><|start_header_id|>user<|end_header_id|>\n\nThat sounds like a reasonable proposal. I think I can live with taking all three rings. However, I'd like to confirm that this proposal works for both of us before we finalize it. Can you confirm that you're happy with taking the pan and the dice, and I'll take the three rings?<|eot_id|><|start_header_id|>assistant<|end_header_id|>\n\nYes, I'm happy with taking the pan and the dice. I think this division works well for both of us. I'll make my secret proposal accordingly.<|eot_id|><|start_header_id|>user<|end_header_id|>\n\nThe other player has submitted a secret proposal. It is now your turn to submit a proposal of your own.<|eot_id|><|start_header_id|>assistant<|end_header_id|>\n\n[Proposal: 1 pan, 1 dice]<|eot_id|>",
